    "description": "《Funko Fusion》是款让粉丝们互动的第三人称动作游戏。操控来自电视剧，电影，电子游戏与漫画的不同角色。探索受到Jurassic World, Back to the Future, JAWS, The Thing, Chucky, Battlestar Galactica, Hot Fuzz, The Umbrella Academy, Five Nights at Freddy’s, Masters of the Universe, Invincible等大作启发的迷人世界，还有更多惊喜！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/ca6ae364bb3262a1603be552bd675b0f.poster.avif?t=1763993341\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/ca6ae364bb3262a1603be552bd675b0f.webm?t=1763993341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/ca6ae364bb3262a1603be552bd675b0f.mp4?t=1763993341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>来自超过20款作品、超过60种可玩角色将以Funko Pop!公仔的形式重现。尽情表达您的热情吧。<br><br>挥舞每个角色的武器，展示他们的技能。部分角色拥有解决谜题和寻找秘密的独特技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/55b4942896bb34a4417f56d987d7ea76.poster.avif?t=1763993341\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/55b4942896bb34a4417f56d987d7ea76.webm?t=1763993341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/55b4942896bb34a4417f56d987d7ea76.mp4?t=1763993341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您可以在其中重温您最喜爱的电影、电视剧、漫画等中的经典时刻。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/412f005745fdfc33ef66c64642569346.poster.avif?t=1763993341\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/412f005745fdfc33ef66c64642569346.webm?t=1763993341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843310/extras/412f005745fdfc33ef66c64642569346.mp4?t=1763993341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>透过远程射击，近距战斗压制敌人。 制作不一样的道具突破难关及寻找隐藏关卡。",
